55134350-c884-4002-bb5d-16337aaa0aaa.title: Veos
55134350-c884-4002-bb5d-16337aaa0aaa.text: Great, I'll take it off your hands now.

05cc246a-b012-4be8-9367-10f9a638515a.text: You give Veos the Ancient Casket

3555af03-600a-4cb6-a86f-b5ddcabbba1b.title: Veos
3555af03-600a-4cb6-a86f-b5ddcabbba1b.text:
Brilliant. This is just what I was looking for. Thank you
so much for your help.

9d1124ac-5ae2-44b2-8c30-dae774dcb823.title: <player>
9d1124ac-5ae2-44b2-8c30-dae774dcb823.text: No problem. So what is this treasure anyway?

17db7d4d-52a9-44f4-82c0-6d44cab065c5.title: Veos
17db7d4d-52a9-44f4-82c0-6d44cab065c5.text:
Oh err... nothing important. Just something that might
be of use to me back in Great Kourend.

0047bc58-ba2d-43a6-bfa7-f127bf8960f2.title: Veos
0047bc58-ba2d-43a6-bfa7-f127bf8960f2.text: Anyway, as promised, a reward for you.

2d9c5f18-61eb-49d9-a298-3682eada2999.title: Veos
2d9c5f18-61eb-49d9-a298-3682eada2999.text:
Anyway, I'd best be getting back to Great Kourend.
I'm sure I'll be back here before long though, there's
always more treasure to be found.

4139e05f-a44b-4f1c-93d2-96b756ae7c65.title: Veos
4139e05f-a44b-4f1c-93d2-96b756ae7c65.text:
If you ever fancy visiting the kingdom, come find me
here. I'm more than happy to take you there. Consider
it an extra thank you for your help.

c91a4e7f-eb61-463f-9380-34aefc0ed836.title: <player>
c91a4e7f-eb61-463f-9380-34aefc0ed836.text: I found the treasure, But I don't have it with me.

2d79601d-27ce-4691-a69a-5108b9349c8d.title: Veos
2d79601d-27ce-4691-a69a-5108b9349c8d.text: Well could you go and get it then?

05aeef80-df1a-474f-ae39-c62b31745110.title: Veos
05aeef80-df1a-474f-ae39-c62b31745110.text:
I came across this scroll. Did you lose it by any
chance?

06b1430e-e07f-4e3c-9256-1e527433697b.text: Veos has given you a scroll.

8a4924d3-575b-4a60-8ee4-7c6c54d8ae6b.title: Veos
8a4924d3-575b-4a60-8ee4-7c6c54d8ae6b.text: Not to worry. Just try to be careful with it.

cda9c36b-a1af-4701-8a18-7b6eced72e5a.title: Required
cda9c36b-a1af-4701-8a18-7b6eced72e5a.text: Talking to Veos before starting the quest

df747444-8840-4e00-be28-348264acfb2f.title: Veos
df747444-8840-4e00-be28-348264acfb2f.text: Hello there. What can I do for you?

options.text: Can you take me to Great Kourend?
Tell me more about Great Kourend.

cb1ab3b5-4d36-406d-aaf2-eea01983abf5.title: <player>
cb1ab3b5-4d36-406d-aaf2-eea01983abf5.text: Can you take me to Great Kourend?

ce3000e6-058e-45b5-9add-2225d2fa9bc1.title: Veos
ce3000e6-058e-45b5-9add-2225d2fa9bc1.text:
Unfortunately, at this time it is impossible to
bring you to Great Kourend as the team has
not yet created Zeah, the continent which Great
Kourend resides. Check back at another time!

b7772dff-1161-4f9d-b5f7-ea9104ba71f6.title: <player>
b7772dff-1161-4f9d-b5f7-ea9104ba71f6.text: Tell me more about Great Kourend.

ea53bbb8-6844-4f8f-9105-73a933117c13.title: Veos
ea53bbb8-6844-4f8f-9105-73a933117c13.text:
Great Kourend is a magnificent kingdom comprising of
five cities. They are the cities of Arceuus, Lovakengj,
Shayzien, Piscarilius and Hosidius. Each city is ruled
by one of the five houses of Kourend.

fcf331f6-9274-4501-b5d4-2e33a57181e9.title: Veos
fcf331f6-9274-4501-b5d4-2e33a57181e9.text:
At one time, the kingdom as a whole was ruled over by
a king or queen that the five houses answered to.

7edbbd5e-74ab-43d5-a825-eaedcaa3b92c.title: Veos
7edbbd5e-74ab-43d5-a825-eaedcaa3b92c.text:
However, since the last King died 20 years ago, the
kingdom has instead been ruled by the Kourend
Council.

options.text: That's great, can you take me there please?

fcc6cca7-2ba9-4c6a-8240-714fccf49a2b.title: <player>
fcc6cca7-2ba9-4c6a-8240-714fccf49a2b.text: That's great, can you take me there please?
